{
  "text": "From [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] we know that there exist good nested lattice codes that can achieve the capacity of an AWGN channel. These nested lattice codes have been used to develop the compute-and-forward framework [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] . We utilize this framework as relaying strategy and extend it with secrecy constraints as described above.",
  "correct_citation": {
